Description: # Wordpress Toolbox
        
        ## Description
        
        Command line tools for managing a wordpress website.
        
        ## Installation
        
        ```
        pip install wordpress_toolbox
        
        ## Usage
        
        ```
        wpt --url https://hostname.com get-post 99
        ```
        
        ```
        wpt --url https://hostname.com get-posts
        ```
        
